- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with neural network-based controllers, which is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses learning-enabled components in autonomous systems, which is a topic within machine learning. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The case study involves a Dubins car model of an autonomous vehicle, which is a robotics application. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): While not the main focus, the paper does touch on the security aspect of ensuring safety in cyber-physical systems.
